Throughout his career, Tendai &#8216;The Beast&#8217; Mtawarira has had to tame the most grizzled front rows in world rugby. On Wednesday, he revealed a new challenge: wrestling a huge python. Mtawarira was participating in Cell C&#8217;s new digital reality show, #BreakTheNet, which is looking for the next YouTube sensation. Cell C is the title sponsor of the loosehead prop&#8217;s union, the Sharks. For more sport your way, follow The Citizen on Facebook and Twitter.